categories: Category:Imperial Army personnel of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Leen was a male Human who served as a corporal in the Imperial Army of the reconstituted Sith Empire. During the Battle of Corellia in the Galactic War, he was stationed at the Imperial war camp in the Labor Valley region of the planet Corellia, distributing stimulants and medical supplies to other Imperial forces.
Corporal Leen appears in the massively multiplayer online roleplaying video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Stims Vendor for Imperial players on Corellia.
